'''魏圣美'''（'''{{lang-en|Michelle Wie}}'''，'''{{lang-ko|위성미}}'''，{{bd|1989年|10月11日|catIdx=W魏}}）是[[韓裔美國人|韓裔美國人]]，出生于[[夏威夷|夏威夷]][[火奴鲁鲁|火奴鲁鲁]]，美国职业[[高尔夫球|高尔夫球]]球员。

魏圣美4岁起学习高尔夫球。她是取得美国职业高尔夫球协会锦标赛（15岁）和美国女子职业高尔夫球协会锦标赛（14岁）参赛资格最年轻的球员。她在2005年10月5日16岁生日前夕宣布成为职业选手。她与[[Nike|Nike]]及[[索尼|索尼]]公司的赞助合同金额估计达每年一千万美元以上。2019年《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》統計收入最高的女運動員，魏圣美以年收入530萬美元，排名第15名<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.forbes.com/sites/kurtbadenhausen/2019/08/06/the-highest-paid-female-athletes-2019-serena-and-osaka-dominate/#3681f2312fcc |title = The Highest-Paid Female Athletes 2019: Serena And Osaka Dominate |publisher = Forbes |language = en |accessdate = 2019-12-09 |archive-date = 2019-08-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190829184736/https://www.forbes.com/sites/kurtbadenhausen/2019/08/06/the-highest-paid-female-athletes-2019-serena-and-osaka-dominate/#3681f2312fcc |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

她身高{{height|ft=6|in=1}}，开球有力，推球进洞的能力稍弱。她极受媒体重视，每次比赛都有大量记者和支持她的观众围观。

== 早年生活 ==
魏聖美於[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]出生，為1980年代韓裔移民的後代。魏聖美是家中獨女，父親是[[夏威夷大學|夏威夷大學]]教授，母親於韓國曾經參加[[選美|選美]]，是韓國1985年女子業餘高爾夫球比賽冠軍<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/magazine/4727895.stm |title=Faces of the week / Michelle Wie |work=BBC |date=2005-07-29|access-date=2019-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060426211912/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/magazine/4727895.stm |archive-date=2006-04-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的祖父亦是[[首爾大學|首爾大學]]的名譽教授<ref>{{cite news |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2005/golf/10/11/wie.city/ |title=South Korean town no longer sending money to Wie |agency=Reuters |date=2005-10-11|work=CNN |access-date=2019-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024004938/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2005/golf/10/11/wie.city/ |archive-date=2012-10-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://english.chosun.com/w21data/html/news/200812/200812200001.html |title=Michelle Wie Finds New Mature Confidence |newspaper=[[Chosun_Ilbo|Chosun Ilbo]] |date=2008-12-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090131232403/http://english.chosun.com/w21data/html/news/200812/200812200001.html |archivedate=2009-01-31}}</ref>。魏聖美於出生時擁有雙重國籍，她在2013年2月宣佈放棄韓國國籍<ref>{{cite news |url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/national/2013/02/27/0302000000AEN20130227002300315.HTML |title=U.S.-born golfer Michelle Wie relinquishes S. Korean citizenship: officials |work=[[Yonhap_News|Yonhap News]] |date=2013-02-27|accessdate=2013-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305023724/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/national/2013/02/27/0302000000AEN20130227002300315.HTML |archive-date=2016-03-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

魏聖美2007年6月畢業於[[普納荷學校|普納荷學校]]後，在同年9月於[[史丹佛大學|史丹佛大學]]開始大學生活，但由於她已經是職業高爾夫球手，所以根據[[國家大學體育協會|國家大學體育協會]]規例，不符合加入大學球隊的資格<ref>{{cite news |last=Gyr |first=Alex |title=Wie set to attend Stanford |newspaper=The Stanford Daily |date=2007-01-08|url=http://daily.stanford.edu/article/2007/1/8/wieSetToAttendStanford |accessdate=2007-06-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071013083042/http://daily.stanford.edu/article/2007/1/8/wieSetToAttendStanford |archivedate=2007-10-13}}</ref><ref name="atstanford">{{cite news |last=Bonk |first=Thomas |title=Teeing Off |newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=2007-09-20|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2007/sep/20/sports/sp-teeingoff20 |accessdate=2010-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102041005/http://articles.latimes.com/2007/sep/20/sports/sp-teeingoff20 |archive-date=2012-11-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在學首3年她都只有出席秋冬兩季的課堂<ref name="stanford-calendar">{{cite web |title=Stanford Academic Calendar, 2009-10 |publisher=[[Stanford_University|Stanford University]] |url=http://studentaffairs.stanford.edu/registrar/academic-calendar |accessdate=2010-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203025035/https://studentaffairs.stanford.edu/registrar/academic-calendar |archive-date=2015-12-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，餘下日子都需要請假準備及出席職業比賽<ref name="stanford-leave">{{cite news |last=Benson |first=Jim |title=Wie to play in State Farm Classic |newspaper=[[Pantagraph|Pantagraph.com]] |date=2008-04-15|url=http://www.pantagraph.com/articles/2008/04/15/sportsextra/doc48038fa32bc4d586033572.txt |accessdate=2008-04-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208072656/http://www.pantagraph.com/articles/2008/04/15/sportsextra/doc48038fa32bc4d586033572.txt |archivedate=2008-12-08}}</ref><ref name="qschool09interview">{{cite web |title=LPGA Final Qualifying Tournament Final Round Interviews |publisher=[[LPGA|LPGA]] |date=2008-12-07|url=http://www.lpga.com/content_1.aspx?pid=18418&mid=1#michelle |accessdate=2008-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309160144/http://www.lpga.com/content_1.aspx?pid=18418&mid=1#michelle |archive-date=2012-03-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她2012年傳理系畢業，並於同年6月出席大學畢業典禮<ref name="college-graduation2">{{cite magazine |magazine=[[Golf_Digest|Golf Digest]] |url=http://www.golfdigest.com/golf-tours-news/2012-03/gwar-michelle-wie-education |title=The Education Of Michelle Wie |date=2012-03-19|accessdate=2012-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150811193720/http://www.golfdigest.com/golf-tours-news/2012-03/gwar-michelle-wie-education |archive-date=2015-08-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="college-graduation">{{cite web |publisher=LPGA |url=http://www.lpga.com/content_1.aspx?pid=32340&mid=1#michelle |title=2012 Kia Classic Pre-Tournament Interviews-Michelle Wie |date=2012-03-21|accessdate=2012-03-24}}</ref>。

== 業餘時期（2000至2005年） ==
魏聖美4歲開始打球，於2000年以10歲之齡成為{{le|美國女子業餘公眾林克斯錦標賽|U.S. Women's Amateur Public Links}}年齡最小的入圍者。這紀錄直到8年後，才被同為夏威夷出身的艾里森·科普茲（{{lang|en|Allisen Corpuz}}）打破。艾里森比魏聖美當年小5個月<ref name="TimmonsHanaHou">{{cite magazine |first=Grady |last=Timmons |title=The Power of Michelle |magazine=The Magazine of Hawaiian Airlines |url=http://www.hanahou.com/pages/magazine.asp?Action=DrawArticle&ArticleID=391&MagazineID=24 |accessdate=2009-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307221843/http://www.hanahou.com/pages/Magazine.asp?Action=DrawArticle&ArticleID=391&MagazineID=24 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。魏聖美為該錦標賽年紀最小參賽者的紀錄，至2014年才被比她當年小1星期的香港移民後裔{{le|李億 (高爾夫球手)|Lucy Li|李億}}（{{lang|en|Lucy Li}}）所破<ref>{{cite news|url=http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20140522/00423_046.html|title=港移民11歲女創紀錄|date=2014-05-22|publisher=太陽報}}</ref><ref name=L1TBINSA>{{cite web|url=http://www.usga.org/news/2014/April/Drive,-Chip-and-Putt--Lucy-Li/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140520221352/http://www.usga.org/news/2014/April/Drive,-Chip-and-Putt--Lucy-Li/|archive-date=2014-05-20|title=Li, 11, To Be In National Spotlight Again |accessdate=2014-05-20|date=2014-04-04|publisher=[[United_States_Golf_Association|United States Golf Association]] |last=Shefter |first=David }}</ref>。

2001年，11歲的魏聖美贏得夏威夷州女子比桿賽（{{lang|en|Hawaii State Women's Stroke Play Championship}}）和珍妮·威爾遜女士邀請賽（{{lang|en|Jennie K. Wilson Women's Invitational}}）冠軍，當中珍妮·威爾遜女士邀請賽是夏威夷歷史最悠久而且最負盛名的業餘高爾夫球比賽<ref name="TimmonsHanaHou"/>。

2002年，她在夏威夷州公開賽女子組，以13桿的差距贏得冠軍。她亦成為年紀最輕入圍[[美國女子職業高爾夫協會|LPGA]]賽事的選手。她最終沒有拿到出賽資格，但她的紀錄一直保持至2007年，才被當時11歲的泰國籍選手{{le|艾莉雅·茱塔努岡|Ariya Jutanugarn}}（{{lang|en|Ariya Jutanugarn}}）所破<ref name="ariyarecord">{{cite web |title=Han returns to defend Honda LPGA Thailand 2007 |publisher=LPGA |date=2007-10-22|url=http://www.lpga.com/content_1.aspx?pid=13119&mid=1 |accessdate=2009-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324102757/http://www.lpga.com/content_1.aspx?pid=13119&mid=1 |archive-date=2012-03-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="takefujiscore">{{cite news |title=Twelve-year-old misses cut, but not the fun |agency=Associated Press |work=ESPN |date=2002-03-01|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/print?id=1343825&type=Story&imagesPrint=off |accessdate=2009-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102151859/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/print?id=1343825&type=Story&imagesPrint=off |archive-date=2012-11-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2003年於[[全日空锦标赛|卡夫納貝斯克錦標賽]]，她終於取得LPGA賽事的出賽資格，並刷新了LPGA賽事年紀最輕出賽者的紀錄。同年6月，她贏得美國女子業餘公眾林克斯錦標賽冠軍，成為贏得[[美國高爾夫協會|USGA]]成人賽事最年輕的選手（不論男女），及取得[[美國女子公開賽|美國女子公開賽]]的入圍資格，她當年只有13歲<ref name="usopen2003record">{{cite web |publisher=michellewiefans.com |title=Career summary 2003 |date=2008-01-15|url=http://www.michellewiefans.com/summary/2003.htm |accessdate=2008-02-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081120144649/http://www.michellewiefans.com/summary/2003.htm |archivedate=2008-11-20}}</ref>。

2005年10月5日，在16歲生日的1星期之前，她宣佈轉打職業賽，並與[[Nike|Nike]]及[[索尼|索尼]]公司簽署金額估計達每年一千萬美元的贊助合同。

== 職業時期 ==
=== 成為LPGA會員之前（2005至2008年） ===
由於[[美國女子職業高爾夫協會|美國女子職業高爾夫協會]]規定其會員最低年齡為18歲，而魏聖美又沒有仿效{{le|摩根·普蕾索|Morgan Pressel}}及{{le|宋雅莉|Aree Song}}等選手申請年齡豁免，所以她在成年之前只可以有限度參與LPGA賽事。

2006年，她成為繼[[朴世莉|朴世莉]]之後第二位出賽{{le|SK電訊公開賽|SK Telecom Open}}（男子賽事）的女子，據報她的出賽酬金比該比賽的總獎金還要多<ref name="koreatripmoney">{{cite web |title=Michelle Wie's 10-Day Korea Trip to Net Her US$5 million |publisher=Digital Chosunilbo |date=2006-04-20|url=http://english.chosun.com/w21data/html/news/200604/200604200008.html |accessdate=2006-04-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060422002748/http://english.chosun.com/w21data/html/news/200604/200604200008.html |archivedate=2006-04-22}}</ref>。

=== LPGA會員（2009年至今） ===
2009年11月15日，她在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]的{{le|奧查婭邀請賽|Lorena Ochoa Invitational}}，以低[[標準桿|標準桿]]13桿的成績，贏得個人第一個職業賽冠軍<ref name="66tournament">{{cite web |website=www.golf.co.uk |title=Wie Claims Maiden LPGA Tour Victory |date=2009-11-15|url=http://www.golf.co.uk/news/wie_claims_maiden_lpga_tour_victory/266509.shtml |accessdate=2009-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301071103/http://www.golf.co.uk/news/wie_claims_maiden_lpga_tour_victory/266509.shtml |archive-date=2012-03-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="LPGALeaderboard">{{cite web |publisher=LPGA |title=Final Results Lorena Ochoa Invitational |date=2009-11-15|url=http://www.lpga.com/content_1.aspx?pid=22509&mid=1 |accessdate=2009-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629123544/http://www.lpga.com/content_1.aspx?pid=22509&mid=1 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="APWireWieWinOne">{{cite news |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |title=Wie Earns First L.P.G.A. Victory; Woods Wins in Australia |date=2009-11-15 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/16/sports/golf/16golf.html |accessdate=2015-01-13|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180127104656/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/16/sports/golf/16golf.html |archive-date=2018-01-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年12月，於{{le|歐洲女子巡迴賽|Ladies European Tour}}賽季最後一場的{{le|迪拜女子大師賽|Omega Dubai Moonlight Classic}}奪亞，以低標準桿15桿的完成賽事，以3杆之差輸給{{le|金人卿|In-Kyung Kim}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ladieseuropeantour.info/tic/tmscores.cgi?tourn=TM25~params=PG0SSA999~season=2009~style=00~groupties=Y~bordersize=1~pr=Y~textout=N~cardlink=Y~winfocus=Y~ |title=Final 2009 Dubai Masters Leaderboard |publisher=Ladies European Tour |access-date=2010-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100302120707/http://www.ladieseuropeantour.info/tic/tmscores.cgi?tourn=TM25~params=PG0SSA999~season=2009~style=00~groupties=Y~bordersize=1~pr=Y~textout=N~cardlink=Y~winfocus=Y~ |archive-date=2010-03-02}}</ref>。

2010年8月29日，她在{{le|加拿大女子公開賽|Canadian Women's Open}}以3杆的差距贏得職業生涯第二場賽事<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2010/08/29/1798190/wie-captures-2nd-lpga-tour-win.html |title=Wie captures 2nd LPGA Tour win in Canada |agency=Sports Network |date=2010-08-29|newspaper=[[Miami_Herald|Miami Herald]] |accessdate=2010-08-29}}</ref>。兩星期後，她在{{le|沃爾瑪西北阿肯色錦標賽|Walmart NW Arkansas Championship}}以1杆之微輸給[[台灣|台灣]]選手[[曾雅妮|曾雅妮]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bostonherald.com/sports/golf/view/20100913michelle_wie_short_as_yani_tseng_rallies/ |title=Michelle Wie short as Yani Tseng rallies |newspaper=[[Boston_Herald|Boston Herald]] |date=2010-09-13|access-date=2019-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121005184334/http://bostonherald.com/sports/golf/view/20100913michelle_wie_short_as_yani_tseng_rallies |archive-date=2012-10-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年4月19日，她在[[樂天LPGA錦標賽|樂天LPGA錦標賽]]以兩杆的差距贏得職業生涯第三場賽事。她在最後一場之前還落後{{le|安吉拉·斯坦福|Angela Stanford}}（{{lang|en|Angela Stanford}}）4杆，最後一場以67杆的成績力壓安吉拉的73杆<ref>{{cite web |url=http://espn.go.com/golf/story/_/id/10810474/michelle-wie-wins-lpga-lotte-championship |title=Michelle Wie: First victory since 2010 |work=ESPN |agency=Associated Press |date=2014-04-19|access-date=2019-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502074309/http://espn.go.com/golf/story/_/id/10810474/michelle-wie-wins-lpga-lotte-championship |archive-date=2016-05-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年6月22日，她在[[美國女子公開賽|美國女子公開賽]]贏得職業生涯第四場賽事和首個[[美國女子職業高爾夫球巡迴賽|四大賽]]的冠軍<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/23/sports/golf/michelle-wie-wins-us-womens-open-capturing-first-major.html |title=Michelle Wie Wins U.S. Women's Open, Capturing First Major |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2014-06-22|access-date=2019-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221165635/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/23/sports/golf/michelle-wie-wins-us-womens-open-capturing-first-major.html |archive-date=2018-12-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這場比賽的冠軍，連同她在2014年[[卡夫納貝斯克錦標賽|卡夫納貝斯克錦標賽]]取得亞軍的成績，令她成為首屆[[勞力士安妮卡大賽|勞力士安妮卡大賽]]榮譽獎的得獎者<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/wie-wins-inaugural-annika-major-award/ |title=Wie wins inaugural Annika Major Award |work=Golf Channel |first=Randall |last=Mell |date=2014-09-14|access-date=2014-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140918004955/http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/wie-wins-inaugural-annika-major-award |archive-date=2014-09-18}}</ref>。同年，她亦獲[[ESPN|ESPN]]選為「ESPNW's Impact 25」其中一人<ref>{{cite news |url=http://espn.go.com/espnw/news-commentary/impact25/slideshow/12020053/7/michelle-wie-25-2014-us-women-open-golf-champion |title=2014 espnW Impact 25: Michelle Wie, 25, 2014 U.S. Women's Open Golf Champion |work=ESPN |accessdate=2014-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305072111/http://espn.go.com/espnw/news-commentary/impact25/slideshow/12020053/7/michelle-wie-25-2014-us-women-open-golf-champion |archive-date=2016-03-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

